WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.820
 Omer, what happened? 

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.520
 Guys will soon bring Asly ... 

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.340
 You can take her home. 

00:00:16.340 --> 00:00:19.080
 Thank you very much! 

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.780
 Sorry. 

00:00:42.780 --> 00:00:44.780
 Do not worry. 

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:45.620
 I... 

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:49.060
 I'm so glad I don't understand what I'm doing ... 

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:58.340
 Anyway ... see you later .. 

00:00:58.340 --> 00:01:00.340
 Well see you. 

00:01:00.860 --> 00:01:01.660
 Let everything be in the past! 

00:01:01.940 --> 00:01:02.940
 Thank! 

00:01:07.420 --> 00:01:09.060
 Omer! 

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:14.460
 Yes? 

00:01:16.760 --> 00:01:18.460
 I am sorry. 

00:01:19.060 --> 00:01:21.260
 Well, I said, do not worry. 

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:27.160
 No ... not for this .... not for being hugged. 

00:01:27.320 --> 00:01:29.220
 For a hug, too, I apologize ... that is ... 

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:30.420
 Good, good ... do not panic! 

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:32.220
 All apologies accepted. 

00:01:33.620 --> 00:01:35.840
 I was rude to you because I thought you hadn't kept your promise ... 

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:38.240
 But I learned that it is not. 

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:42.340
 You called me. I want to say, what else could you do? 

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:46.680
 I apologize. 

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.760
 No problem... 

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:50.760
 I was not offended. 

00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:52.280
 It happens... 

00:01:54.940 --> 00:01:56.880
 Do you want to say anything more? 

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:01.940
 You will not scold, reproach and do not say "I will never forget", or something like that 

00:02:02.020 --> 00:02:03.940
 I will say ... 

00:02:05.940 --> 00:02:08.360
 That happens. 

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:18.220
 You improve your italian 

00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:23.340
 Thank you for understanding. 

00:02:34.540 --> 00:02:37.380
 Do not exaggerate. 

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:39.860
 We are friends. 

00:02:52.020 --> 00:02:55.340
 Well done, Omer! Well done! 

00:02:55.340 --> 00:02:57.340
 Well done! 

